Mr. Lee!

8
00:02:42,190 --> 00:02:44,200
Take care.

9
00:02:44,200 --> 00:02:46,330
I said I'll give you a share of land.

10
00:02:46,330 --> 00:02:49,110
Later. If you get the share, come back then.

11
00:02:49,110 --> 00:02:50,790
Please leave now for today.

12
00:02:50,790 --> 00:02:54,080
- Take care!
- I said I can leave on my own!

13
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:56,620
Gosh, seriously!

14
00:02:59,310 --> 00:03:02,750
Look at you, smiling like this.

15
00:03:02,750 --> 00:03:07,060
You don't even know what this is. Geez.

16
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:10,200
Hello.

17
00:03:10,200 --> 00:03:14,900
Attorney Cho, show up earlier.
Do I need to tend to stuff like this?

18
00:03:15,760 --> 00:03:17,550
Geez.

19
00:03:22,460 --> 00:03:25,990
Well, what's going on?

20
00:03:27,390 --> 00:03:29,540
I understand what you mean.

21
00:03:29,540 --> 00:03:31,700
But I can't because I have too much to do.

22
00:03:31,700 --> 00:03:34,100
- Please visit somewhere else.
- Geez.

23
00:03:34,100 --> 00:03:36,430
Are you the only attorney here?

24
00:03:36,430 --> 00:03:38,260
Give it to another attorney.

25
00:03:38,260 --> 00:03:40,790
Well, we're a small firm.

26
00:03:40,790 --> 00:03:44,200
Hey. I said I'll give you a share of land!

27
00:03:44,200 --> 00:03:47,190
- I'm so sorry.
- Geez.

28
