810
01:05:28,050 --> 01:05:30,090
Oh, okay.

811
01:05:33,580 --> 01:05:35,290
Come on in.

812
01:05:36,020 --> 01:05:37,390
Did you want to see me, Mr. Seong?

813
01:05:37,390 --> 01:05:41,310
