814
01:05:41,310 --> 01:05:43,120
Long time no see.

815
01:05:47,570 --> 01:05:48,640
Hello.

816
01:05:48,640 --> 01:05:50,540
Have a seat.

817
01:05:50,540 --> 01:05:54,380
He came to give you a case.

818
01:05:54,380 --> 01:05:59,500
I got into a car accident
