819
01:05:59,500 --> 01:06:01,560
I'm in your care.

820
01:06:01,560 --> 01:06:03,910
You're my personal attorney.

821
01:06:14,560 --> 01:06:17,140
Hello, sir.

822
01:06:17,140 --> 01:06:20,070
Gosh, wait, wait, wait.

823
01:06:20,070 --> 01:06:22,130
Wait, wait.

824
01:06:22,130 --> 01:06:24,740
Attorney Ha, you just arrived.

825
01:06:24,740 --> 01:06:27,260
Well, yes. Hello.

826
01:06:29,480 --> 01:06:30,980
Good morning.

827
01:06:30,980 --> 01:06:32,630
Yes.

828
01:06:44,420 --> 01:06:47,560
He apparently hit someone lightly.

829
01:06:47,560 --> 01:06:50,590
It wasn't a serious accident. It won't be hard.

830
01:06:50,590 --> 01:06:52,170
You're telling me to take the case, right?

831
01:06:52,170 --> 01:06:53,640
Of course, you should.

832
01:06:53,640 --> 01:06:56,630
Director Jang brought the case to you.

833
01:07:01,420 --> 01:07:04,000
I won't take it.

834
01:07:04,000 --> 01:07:07,000
- What?
