836
01:07:10,420 --> 01:07:12,080
You can take it or...

837
01:07:12,080 --> 01:07:14,440
tell him to find another attorney somewhere else.

838
01:07:14,440 --> 01:07:16,620
Do as you wish.

839
01:07:18,050 --> 01:07:21,490
